extendedInfo.description: Game TestA Dalmatian dog runs away from home.You must blow the whistle to get him back home.On the way you will have to help him collect and eat the bones, so you have to match his head under the bone and stop whistle, if the location is convenient, the dog will eat the bone and stop, otherwise you will lose a life.Watch the video to see how it plays. Have fun!dalmatian, dog, game, pet, whistle
